item.title: [REQ]Interface command
item.dc:creator: @runescape_sucks runescape sucks
item.description:
@runescape_sucks wrote:

if it’s pi its probably

c.getPA().showInterface(id);

or

c.getPA().sendInterface(id);

if you’re referencing the player as c that is.
